<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>Dear <%= @student.full_name %>,</p>
    <p>Here are your results for the assessments done during the semester starting <%= @assessment.full_semester_name %>.</p>
    <table style="border: 1px solid black; border-style: collapse;">
      <thead style="background-color: #F36B08;color: white;">
        <th style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 10px;">Unit</th>
        <th style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 10px;">Attendance</th>
        <th style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 10px;">Assignments</th>
        <th style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 10px;">CAT Practical</th>
        <th style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 10px;">CAT Theory</th>
        <th style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 10px;">Final Practical</th>
        <th style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 10px;">Final Theory</th>
        <th style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 10px;">Assessment</th>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <% @results.each do |result| %>
          <tr style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 10px;">
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 10px;"><%= result.unit.full_unit_name %></td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 10px;"><%= result.attendance %></td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 10px;"><%= result.assignments %></td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 10px;"><%= result.cat_practical %></td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 10px;"><%= result.cat_theory %></td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 10px;"><%= result.final_practical %></td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 10px;"><%= result.final_theory %></td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 10px;"><%= result.final_assessment.humanize %></td>
          </tr>
        <%end%>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <br/>
    <p>Kindly contact admin for any queries.</p>
    <br/>
    <i style="font-size: 10pt">Please do not reply to this email.</i>
    <br/>
    <br/>
    <br/>
    <img src="https://i.ibb.co/1KPxv6p/FRONTLEARN-LOGO.png" style="display:block" alt="logo" width="60" height="60" />
    <p><i>Frontlearn Institute AMS</i></p>
    <a href= "www.frontlearn.co.ke"><i>www.frontlearn.co.ke</i></a>
  </body>
</html>